#!/usr/bin/env python3
# ============================================================
# SelahOS Recovery Center
# Accessible from KDE Application Menu → System → SelahOS Recovery
# Runs on the INSTALLED system (not just live ISO)
#
# Provides:
# 1. System Health Check — shows what's installed/working
# 2. SelahBridge Repair — reinstalls Wine/DXVK/WineASIO
# 3. Audio Repair — fixes PipeWire/JACK issues
# 4. Theme Restore — reapplies SelahOS KDE theme
# 5. Fresh Install Helper — guides reinstall from USB
#
# Copyright (C) 2026 Selah Technologies LLC
# ============================================================

